posts.text:
Sendy founder Meshack Alloys: The firm is one of the start-ups training in South Africa. file photo | nmg  By STELLAR MURUMBA 
More by this Author Summary Digital acceleration programme runs for 14 days from November 6 in Cape Town. Kenyan entrepreneurs offering digital solutions make a group of 20 others in the region to benefit from the World Bank Digital Acceleration Program in South Africa. The entrepreneurs will — under the XL Africa residency — be mentored in the flagship initiative of the business accelerator launched last April by the World Bank. It will run from November 6 to 17 in Cape Town, giving them access to potential corporate partners and investors. The start-ups offer digital solutions for the African market, including fin-tech, transportation, health care, education, human resources, and business to business. The Kenyan start-ups include delivery apps Sendy Ltd and Soko Watch, HR platform Lynk Jobs Limited, SME services platform Ongair and Pesabazaar.com, a fintech company. Others are Snapplify, a publishing app with presence in Kenya and South Africa, and Asoko Insight, a data firm operating in Kenya, Ethiopia, Ghana, United Kingdom, and Nigeria. “We encountered strong companies, particularly in the transportation, HR, and data analytics sectors,” said Danai Musandu, investment associate at Goodwell Investments. “We also observed signals of a nascent pipeline of digital companies beyond the traditional hot spots of Nigeria, Kenya, and South Africa.” Klaus Tilmes, the director of trade and competitiveness global practice at the World Bank said XL Africa will help the start-ups attract early stage capital of between Sh25.8 million and Sh154.5 million. XL Africa is funded by the governments of Finland, Norway, and Sweden, and administered by the World Bank with implementation support from IMC Worldwide, VC4A, and Koltai & Co. Other startups were picked from Senegal, Benin, Tanzania, Nigeria and South Africa.

posts.title: 울산 민주당 '제명 내홍'에 한국당 역공 "적폐 말할 자격있나" 뉴스
posts.text:
제명된 한동수 폭로 기자회견 두고 한국당 가세
[오마이뉴스 박석철 기자]
▲ 7일 오전 11시 30분 자유한국당 천기옥 울산시의원과 울산시당 대변인단이 민주당 울산시당 내홍과 관련한 기자회견을 열고 있다 ⓒ 박석철
문재인 정부 출범 이후 더불어민주당(아래 민주당) 울산시당에 보수 성향의 인사 등 수만 명이 입당하면서 외연이 확장되자 일각에서는 우려의 목소리도 나왔다. 결국 이 우려가 현실화되고 있다.
최근 민주당 울산시당이 "한동수 한반도경제특별위원장이 임동호 시당위원장과 사무처장을 비난하는 현수막 수십 개를 시내 곳곳에 게재해 허위사실을 유포하고 명예를 훼손했다"며 지난 6일 제명하자 한 위원장이 7일 울산시당의 문제점을 폭로하는 기자회견을 열었다. (관련기사 : 민주당, 지방선거 앞두고 문전성시... 울산에선 '제명' 사태
이에 다시 자유한국당 울산시당이 기자회견에서 제시된 내용을 근거로 의혹을 제기하며 역공세에 나섰다. 한국당은 한 위원장이 7일 기자회견에서 밝힌 내용 등을 근거로 선관위 조사와 민주당의 철저한 진상규명을 촉구하고 나섰다.
민주당의 급격한 당원 확대에 한동안 긴장하던 한국당이 민주당의 내홍으로 역공세에 나서면서 지방선거를 7개월 앞두고 사태는 커지는 모양새다.
제명된 민주당 당원 한동수씨 폭로성 기자회견... 한국당은 역공
지난 1일과 2일 민주당 울산시당은 윤리위와 상무위를 잇따라 열고 한동수 위원장을 제명했다. 이에 한 위원장은 한차례 연기 끝에 지난 6일 오전 11시 울산시의회 프레스센터에서 기자회견을 열고 갖가지 의혹을 제기했다.
그는 "민주당 울산시당이 자신들의 잘못은 반성하지 않고 다른 사람에게 뒤집어 씌워서 유언비어나 만들어 퍼트리고 변명하기에 급급하다"면서 "윤리위원 및 상무위원도 진실을 정확하게 파악하지 않고 하루만에 졸속회의로 제명을 했다. 회의록을 공개해야 한다"고 주장했다.
특히 그는 "원인 제공자가 집권여당의 최고위원이고 중앙당 조직국에 소속된 사무처장이라고 아무런 처벌도 하지 않고 있다. 매월 3만원씩 당비를 내는 당원은 옳은 소리 한마디 했다가 제명됐다"면서 중앙당에 제출한 진정서를 공개했다.
진정서에는 최근 울주군 지역위원장 추천을 둘러싼 잡음과 전기 자전거와 꿀 등을 상납한 일, 울산시당이 공기업 자리를 제공하려 했다는 의혹, 내년 지방선거를 앞둔 시의원 공천 문제 등이 담겨 있다.
이에 민주당 울산시당은 즉각 입장을 내고 "11월 1일 2차례 윤리심판위원회에서 한동수 당원 제명을 만장일치로 의결했고 2일 상무위원회의에서 한동수 당원의 불법 현수막 게첩 건이 사실관계를 의도적으로 호도함으로써 시당위원장, 울산시당에 대한 명예훼손이 심각하다고 판단해 제명했다"면서 "명예훼손 등 민형사상의 법적 대응은 법률자문단과 논의해 진행할 계획"이라고 밝혔다.
그러면서 "한동수씨의 목적은 오로지 분란을 일으키는 것이다. 분란을 위해 없는 사실도 만들어야 하고 사실관계도 왜곡하는 것"이라면서 "울산시당은 그의 분란 조장에 조금의 협조도 할 생각이 없으며 예정대로 법적대응을 준비중"이라고 주장했다.
민주당 내의 공방을 지켜보고 있던 자유한국당 울산시당이 가세했다. 한국당 울산시당 여성위원회와 대변인단은 7일 오전 11시 30분 울산시의회에서 기자회견을 열고 "어제(6일) 폭로 기자회견에서 '입당 원서를 금품으로 매수했다'는 내용의 휴대전화 녹음파일이 공개됐다"면서 "의혹으로 남겨서는 안 되며 진실을 끝까지 밝혀야 한다. 더불어민주당이 이 의혹을 철저히 밝혀달라"며 중앙당을 끌어들이는 모습을 보였다.
특히 한국당은 "선관위가 입당원서 금품매수 의혹에 대해 철저히 진상을 밝혀야 한다"면서 "한동수씨가 폭로한 공공기관 인사전횡도 정권차원에서 사죄해야 한다"고 공세 수위를 높였다.
또한 한국당 울산시당 천기옥 시의원은 "'(현수막에 게재된) 여성당원은 5시 이후 어디에서 만나라'라는 입에 담지도 못할 여성 비하 문구가 울산 전역에 도배되다시피 했다"면서 "민주당 울산시당은 시민에게 사과하라"고 촉구했다.
그러면서 "민주당과 관계기관이 나서서 민주주의를 망치고 여성을 비하하고 국정을 뿌리채 흔드는 의혹들의 진상을 낱낱이 밝혀주기를 요청한다"면서 "민주당은 여성 문제와 여성정책에 대해 말할 자격이 없다. 적폐청산, 여성권익 이런 단어들은 언급하지 말아달라"고 요구했다.
이처럼 민주당 울산시당의 급격한 당원 증가로 인해 불거진 당원 제명과 이에 따른 폭로전이 자유한국당에 공격의 빌미를 제공하면서 앞으로 민주당 울산시당과 중앙당이 어떻게 대처할지가 주목된다.

تشهد فعاليات اليوم الثاني لمنتدى شباب العالم الذي يقام في شرم الشيخ العديد من الجلسات، يتحدث فيها 6 شخصيات بارزة، وهم: رئيس تشاد، إدريس أيبي، الذي يشارك في جلسة تحديات وقضايا تواجه شباب العالم.. سبل المواجهة لصناعة المستقبل، ويشاركه هيروتاكا كويني، رئيس منظمة شبابية من اليابان، وميريد دويسك mired dusek من سويسرا، رئيس قسم الشرق الأوسط، وشمال أفريقيا، عضو اللجنة التنفيذية بالمنتدى الاقتصادي العالمي.
أخبار متعلقة
السيسي يصل مركز المؤتمرات الدولي لحضور جلسة «تحديات تواجه شباب العالم»
حوار السيسي مع شبكة «CNBC» الأمريكية (نص كامل)
هل يترشح السيسي لفترة رئاسية ثالثة؟ إجابة قاطعة من الرئيس

ويشارك في ذات الجلسة إرنستو يا ردا، وزير الشباب والرياضة بإثيوبيا، في حين يشارك هون موسيس، وزير الشباب والرياضة الزامبي في جلسة الحوار بين الأجيال، وشما بنت سهيل، وزيرة الدولة للشباب من الإمارات، في جلسة تعزيز مشاركة الشباب في صنع واتخاذ القرار.

Felt by persons at rest, on upper floors or favorably placed. MMI III (Weak shaking) ? People : Felt indoors; hanging objects may swing, vibration similar to passing of light trucks, duration may be estimated, may not be recognized as an earthquake. MMI IV (Light shaking) ? People :Generally noticed indoors but not outside. Light sleepers may be awakened. Vibration may be likened to the passing of heavy traffic, or to the jolt of a heavy object falling or striking the building. Fittings :Doors and windows rattle. Glassware and crockery rattle. Liquids in open vessels may be slightly disturbed. Standing motorcars may rock. Structures :Walls and frames of buildings, and partitions and suspended ceilings in commercial buildings, may be heard to creak. MMI V (Moderate shaking) Generally felt outside, and by almost everyone indoors. Most sleepers awakened. A few people alarmed. Fittings :Small unstable objects are displaced or upset. Some glassware and crockery may be broken. Hanging pictures knock against the wall. Open doors may swing. Cupboard doors secured by magnetic catches may open. Pendulum clocks stop, start, or change rate. Structures :Some large display windows cracked. A few earthenware toilet fixtures cracked. MMI VI (Strong shaking) ? People Felt by all. People and animals alarmed. Many run outside. Difficulty experienced in walking steadily. Fittings :Objects fall from shelves. Pictures fall from walls. Some furniture moved on smooth floors, some unsecured free-standing fireplaces moved. Glassware and crockery broken. Very unstable furniture overturned. Small church and school bells ring. Appliances move on bench or table tops. Filing cabinets or "easy glide" drawers may open (or shut). Structures :Slight damage to buildings with low standard. Some stucco or cement plaster falls. Large display windows broken. Damage to a few weak domestic chimneys, some may fall. Environment :Trees and bushes shake, or are heard to rustle. Loose material may be dislodged from sloping ground, e.g. existing slides, talus slopes, shingle slides. MMI VII (Very strong shaking) ? General alarm. Difficulty experienced in standing. Noticed by motorcar drivers who may stop. Fittings :Large bells ring. Furniture moves on smooth floors, may move on carpeted floors. Substantial damage to fragile contents of buildings. Structures :Unreinforced stone and brick walls cracked. Low standard buildings cracked with some minor masonry falls. A few instances of damage to buildings of ordinary workmanship. Unbraced parapets, unbraced brick gables, and architectural ornaments fall. Roofing tiles, especially ridge tiles may be dislodged. Many unreinforced domestic chimneys damaged, often falling from roof-line. Water tanks Type I burst. A few instances of damage to brick veneers and plaster or cement-based linings. Unrestrained water cylinders (hot-water cylinders) may move and leak. Some common windows cracked. Suspended ceilings damaged. Environment :Water made turbid by stirred up mud. Small slides such as falls of sand and gravel banks, and small rock-falls from steep slopes and cuttings. Instances of settlement of unconsolidated or wet, or weak soils. Some fine cracks appear in sloping ground. A few instances of liquefaction (i.e. small water and sand ejections). MMI VIII (Severe shaking) ? People Alarm may approach panic. Steering of motorcars greatly affected. Structures : Low standard buildings heavily damaged, some collapse. ordinary workmanship buildings damaged, some with partial collapse. Reinforced masonry or concrete buildings damaged in some cases. A few instances of damage to buildings and bridges designed and built to resist earthquakes. Monuments and pre-1976 elevated tanks and factory stacks twisted or brought down. Some pre-1965 infill masonry panels damaged. A few post-1980 brick veneers damaged. Decayed timber piles of houses damaged. Houses not secured to foundations may move. Most unreinforced domestic chimneys damaged, some below roof-line, many brought down. Environment : Cracks appear on steep slopes and in wet ground. Small to moderate slides in roadside cuttings and unsupported excavations. Small water and sand ejections and localized lateral spreading adjacent to streams, canals, lakes, etc. MMI IX (Violent shaking) ? Structures Many low standard buildings destroyed. Ordinary workmanship buildings heavily damaged, some collapse. Reinforced masonry or concrete buildings damaged, some with partial collapse. Buildings and bridges designed and built to resist earthquakes damaged in some cases, some with flexible frames seriously damaged. Damage or permanent distortion to some buildings and bridges, designed and built to normal use standards. Houses not secured to foundations shifted off. Brick veneers fall and expose frames. Environment : Cracking of ground conspicuous. Landsliding general on steep slopes. Liquefaction effects intensified and more widespread, with large lateral spreading and flow sliding adjacent to streams, canals, lakes, etc. Tell us your experience and how many seconds the shaking lasted + let us know if your property has been damaged (even slight damage). posts.text:
Um agricultor morreu esfaqueado no final da tarde desse domingo (05/11), na cidade de Jupi, no Agreste de Pernambuco. 
A vítima ainda deu entrada no hospital, mas não resistiu aos ferimentos e morreu. De acordo com informações da polícia, a família informou que José Berlamino dos Anjos, 41 anos de idade, estava no campo de futebol, quando foi surpreendido pelo acusado Luiz Lidemizio da Silva, armado com uma faca peixeira e desferiu vários golpes na vitima. 
Ainda de acordo com a família, o crime esta relacionado com uma ex-companheira de Luiz, que estaria tendo um caso com José Berlamino. Após o crime Luiz se evadiu tomando destino ignorado. 
O corpo da vítima foi encaminhado ao Instituto de Medicina Legal em Caruaru.

OLEH HAFIZAN TAIB 
SHAH ALAM, 7 NOV: Pembinaan bangunan kediaman di atas tanah kerajaan atau tanah pertanian ketika Kerajaan Negeri ditadbir Barisan Nasional (BN) menimbulkan situasi sukar kepada rakyat di Selangor ketika ini. 
Exco   Dato’   berkata, berikutan tindakan itu, ramai di kalangan pembeli rumah di negeri menghadapi kesukaran bagi mendapatkan hak milik strata. 
“Sepatutnya pemaju menbayar premium tanah kepada Kerajaan Negeri dan mendapat hakmilik yang sahaja sebelum dibenarkan membina bangunan kediaman tetapi terdapat pemaju membangunkannya tanpa perlu membayar. 
“Selain itu terdapat pemaju dibenarkan membina bangunan kediaman di atas tanah pertanian, sepatutnya status tanah ditukar terlebih dahulu sebelum pemaju memulakan projek mereka,” katanya ketika menjawab pertanyaan lisan Ahli Dewan Negeri (ADN) Kinrara, Ng Sze Han dalam sidang Dewan Negeri Selangor (DNS), di sini, hari ini. 
Beliau berkata, setakat ini hanya 8,851 skim pembangunan membabitkan 525,025 hakmilik telah memperoleh hakmilik strata manakala 2,307 skim pembangunan sebaliknya. 
Selain isu tanah, katanya, antara punca itu ialah bangunan yang tiada Sijil Layak Menduduki (CF) atau Perakuan Siap Dan Pematuhan (CCC) dan bangunan dibina terlebih dari sempadan lot.

posts.title: Cómo mejorar la accesibilidad en Divi
posts.text:
Cómo mejorar la accesibilidad en Divi Inicio » Plugins » Cómo mejorar la accesibilidad en Divi Publicado por Fernando el 7 Nov, 2017 Twitter 
La accesibilidad web es vital para que los contenidos lleguen a todos, y como Divi es uno de los temas más populares del universo WordPress, en concreto el 2º según WP Detector , vamos a ver cómo mejorar la accesibilidad en Divi . 
Para ello nada mejor que valernos de un plugin gratuito que mejora muchos aspectos de accesibilidad en Divi . 
Me refiero a Divi Accessibility , un plugin disponible en el repositorio oficial de WordPress.org. 
Básicamente este plugin te ayuda a cumplir las pautas de accesibilidad para contenido web recogidas en las directrices WCAG 2.0 , una serie de indicaciones con las que garantizar la accesibilidad de los contenidos web . 
Estas directrices no están hechas de cualquier modo, están basadas en un estudio de más de 10 años. 
En concreto, las mejoras de accesibilidad en Divi que incorpora el plugin son las siguientes: Añade los atributos ARIA adecuados Mejora la navegación por teclado en los menús Soluciona etiquetas no disponibles o incorrectamente asignadas Hace que módulos como el Conmutador y el Acordeón se puedan enfocar y ser interactivos con el teclado Añade un trazo visual a los elementos enfocables para la navegación solo por teclado Añade la posibilidad de cambiar el teclado solo en el color de trazado Soluciona las clases del lector de pantalla usadas incorrectamente por Divi Añade un enlace para saltar a la navegación optimizado para el marcado de Divi Integración con Tota11y 
Y su uso es muy sencillo. Solo tienes que instalarlo y, a continuación, pasarte por el nuevo menú de administración Divi > Accessibility para configurar los ajustes que quieras. 
Mi consejo es que actives todos los ajustes, para mejorar la accesibilidad en Divi . 
Así que ya sabes, si usas Divi para tus proyectos, mejora la accesibilidad para que todos puedan disfrutar de tus contenidos. Valora este artículo para mejorar la calidad del blog ... ( 3 votos, promedio: 5,00 de 5) Cargando…

By Chiara fabrizi.chiara@gmail.com access_time 2 giorni ago chat_bubble_outline Leave a comment 
E’ un eugubino di 25 anni, il giovane che venerdì ha trovato e restituito un portafoglio con oltre 1.500 euro in contanti. 
Il gesto di Mattia è stato raccontato dai carabinieri di Gubbio, a cui il ragazzo ha portato il malloppo dopo averlo trovato sul ciglio della strada all’altezza di Cipolleto 
Tutto è successo intorno alle 17: poco prima il proprietario del borsellino lo aveva distrattamente lasciato sul tetto dell’auto dopo aver fatto benzina. Non accorgendosi, è ripartito e ovviamente il portafoglio è caduto poco dopo. Il 25enne dopo averlo raccolto lo ha portato alla stazione dei carabinieri spiegando che una volta, mentre era a caccia, è capitato anche a lui di perderlo e, pure in quell’occasione, “fortunatamente qualche altra brava persona lo ha trovato e me lo ha riconsegnato”. 
A quel punto i militari hanno rintracciato il proprietario, un imprenditore 50enne, che si trovava di passaggio nella zona, arrivato poi in caserma dove ovviamente ha ringraziato il ragazzo protagonista del bel gesto.

Philippine Airlines (PAL) is offering free airlift of critical supplies and relief goods for the rebuilding of Marawi City. 
PAL is flying donations to Cagayan de Oro, for transport by land to Marawi City , through accredited government agencies, SEC-registered foundations, NGOs, non-profit, charitable, civic and religious organizations. 
The program, which covers airlifting of donations within the Philippines only, is flying goods on space availability basis. Priority goods are urgently needed items such as medicines, ready-to-eat halal processed foods and products, mats and blankets, water purification tablets and equipment, hygiene supplies such as baby diapers and other commodities which are not readily sourced in the affected areas. 
Donors may send an email to the PAL Foundation at palfoundation@pal.com.ph indicating the following details – name and contact details of donors/organizations, recipient or consignee, contents and estimate cost of donation, weight, etc. They will be given instructions on the schedule of shipment.

Where will the great American experiment take us? I would rather hope that we are more concerned about where our faith journey takes us. I think that as we get older, with more of our lives in the rearview mirror, we are increasingly excited, if not curious, about what the destination looks like. Anything else is just going back and forth. Repeating the same goings and comings. Off to work, back home from work. Off on vacation, back from vacation. We cannot know with great certainty what our ultimate destination looks like, but we sure know where it will be.
Democracies, historically, run their course within 200-300 years. Guess what, fellow citizens of the good ole U.S.A.? Maybe this great idea, this experiment, this journey from the eastern shores of the Atlantic will weather all of the mistrust, division, fear, and hubris that we have allowed to ferment. Or we will find ourselves as God’s people Israel, in an exile of our own making.
I am profoundly overwhelmed by God’s grace. The vocation I share with my brothers and sisters in Christ, all in ministry, already and still becoming disciples – this I treasure. Being convinced, beyond all seemingly reasonable doubts, that “neither life nor death, neither angels nor demons, neither the present or the future, nor any powers, neither height nor depth, nor anything else in all creation, will be able to separate us from the love of God that is in Christ Jesus our Lord (Romans 8:38-39).
I may have doubts about many temporal things, like evil powers holding sway over our lives. Many things that would likely get me in the proverbial boiling cauldron for bringing up, lest they offend my neighbor of opposite opinion. I am confident that we will all figure this experiment out, as we progress on our one-way destination. I am also confident that God will continue to love us unconditionally !
Pastor Art

Brent crude oil held its gains on Tuesday morning and was 0.11 percent up at $64.34 a barrel. 
Russian stock indexes were also on the rise.

Szkockie jaja w Miłości – Scotch Egg Club  07   Szkockie jaja w Miłości – Scotch Egg Club impreza, klub komediowy, scotcheggclub, zabawa Była Barcelona, Londyn i Meksyk – teraz czas na Warszawę! 28 października br. w Miłości na Kredytowej 9, imprezowaliśmy w iście szkockim stylu. Scotch Egg Club – miejsce stworzone przez charyzmatycznego twórcę whisky Tommy’ego Dewara – jest już w Polsce i zagrzeje tu miejsce aż do połowy grudnia, podwójnie bawiąc wszystkich uczestników! 
Scotch Egg Club to połączenie potężnej dawki śmiechu, szkockiego jedzenia i podwójnie dojrzewającego bursztynowego trunku. Inspiracją tego wyjątkowego cyklu imprez był pełen uroku Tommy Dewar – jeden z założycieli marki Dewar’s. 
Ten lekkoduszny, żartobliwy i charyzmatyczny przedsiębiorca przekształcił małą firmę swojego ojca, w największego eksportera szkockiej whisky na świecie w swoich czasach. Codziennie działał według zasady – Pracuj rano, a baw się wieczorem. Co oznaczało, że w ciągu dnia do perfekcji doprowadzał swoją podwójnie dojrzewającą whisky, a wieczorami oddawał się grom, zabawom i swojemu drugiemu hobby – hodowli kur. 
W Scotch Egg Club bawimy się dokładnie tak, jak lubił robić to Tommy – z humorem i w towarzystwie szkockich jajek, kur i podwójnie leżakowanej whisky. 
Jaja w Miłości Scotch Egg Club przemierzył już pół Europy! Warszawa doczekała się go jesienią. Pierwsza impreza miała miejsce w Miłości na Kredytowej 9 pod koniec września. Publiczność bawiła się na Wieczorze Gier z Klubem Komediowym i poznała także zasady gry w wyjątkowe Chicken Bingo. 
Czym jest Chicken Bingo? To jedna z ulubionych gier Szkotów. Zasady są bardzo proste! Uczestnicy dostają karty z liczbami, a po planszy porusza się mały kurczak-robot, który po krótkim czasie zatrzymuje się na jednej z liczb. Wygrywa ten, co posiada kartę ze szczęśliwym numerem. 
Podczas ostatniej soboty w Miłości, Klub Komediowy i Michał Sufin oddali mikrofon publiczności w klasycznym Nawijaku. Opowiadano najróżniejsze historie i anegdoty z życia, które wygrywały nagrody. Humor Tommy’ego Dewara udzielił się wszystkim gościom w Miłości, bo kolejnym, nawet podwójnym anegdotom nie było końca! Niektórzy twierdzą, że przed imprezą ujrzeli przy stoliku postać Tommy’ego, ze szklanką whisky w dłoni. W menu imprezy pojawiły się natomiast szkockie jaja – jako świetna zakąska do drinków z podwójnie postarzaną whisky Dewar’s. 
Bramy Scotch Egg Club otwarte dla wszystkich 
To nie koniec podwójnej zabawy! Wieczory w Scotch Egg Club pojawią się jeszcze nie raz tej jesieni w Miłości na Kredytowej. 
Będziemy bawić się przy dobrej muzyce, zagramy w Chicken Bingo, spróbujemy szkockich jajek, a solidną dawkę śmiechu zapewnią Stand-Uperzy i członkowie Klubu Komediowego. 
Dniami i nocami można przybywać także do Hali Koszyki, w której otwarta jest strefa Scotch Egg Club Pop-Up Bar. Na otwarciu – 6 października br. – graliśmy w Chicken Bingo oraz obejrzeliśmy show Stand Uperów – Karola Modzelewskiego i Tomasza „Borasa” Borkowskiego. Właśnie tam, co piątek można spróbować ulubionych szkockich jaj Tommy’ego Dewara. 
Na wszystkie imprezy Scotch Egg Club wstęp jest wolny, więc…przybywajcie!

posts.title: 论一个吃货的基本素养：那些食物背后的故事
posts.text:
相传在公元前2世纪的中国汉朝，淮南王刘安发明了豆腐。一位中国的研究者提到，在汉代壁画中出现过制作豆腐的过 程。
已故的篠田统博士是中国食物史的世界权威，根据他的研究，“豆腐”这两个字第一次出现在文献中是在10世纪中期。
“豆腐”是乳腐的对应词。豆腐与乳腐的“腐”并非腐败之意，而是指柔软嫩滑的物质。乳腐是借由酸或酵素的作用，使奶变成略显固态的酸奶或奶酪状的乳制品。
在中国，经常与北方游牧民族往来的唐朝盛行吃乳制品。唐朝人将游牧民族传来的乳腐所使用的动物奶，换成以黄豆为原料的“豆浆”，这样制作出来的就是豆腐。
乳中的蛋白质凝固就成了奶酪，豆腐则是豆浆中的蛋白质凝固而成的食品。
豆腐被视为健康食品后，欧美国家也开始食用，于是日语的“tofu”就成了豆腐的通用语。在那之前，豆腐的英文是“soy bean curd”（黄豆凝乳）。去除水分前刚凝固的奶酪被称为curd，色白软嫩就像豆腐一样。
奈良县的春日大社的供品中有一项名为“唐符”，据说就是日本最早出现的豆 腐。
日本人吃饭时为什么要说“我要开动了”
我曾在一位美国牧师的家里用过餐。当时我听到对方说“Let’s start”（我们开始吧）后，正准备要吃的时候，突然觉得气氛有点奇怪。只见同桌的其他人全都低下了头，牧师口中开始念念有词。原来，“我们开始吧”是指开始餐前的祷告。
如今在欧美国家已经很少有人会这么做，但信奉基督教的人仍有餐前祷告的习惯。虔诚的伊斯兰教教徒将食物放入口中前，也会诵念《古兰经》。
昭和十六年（1941）至昭和十七年（1942），民俗学的研究者们针对全日本五十八个村落的饮食习惯进行了调查。他们事后进行报告检讨时发现，餐前餐后有诵念习惯的村落很少，大概只有两个村子的人会先说“南无阿弥陀佛”再用餐。
可是，餐前餐后合掌不语，或是拿起碗筷时会先低下头再进食的习惯，却在这些村中都很普及。在神坛或佛坛供奉米饭，也是很普通的事，用餐时要向神佛、祖先表示感谢，是在家庭中养成的习惯。
报告中也提到，“举筷时谨记天地圣泽、君王父母之恩，我要开动了”这句诵念文是孩子们在学校里学到的话。这是因为在战争期间，校方让孩子们吃便当前诵念这句话。
养成在餐前餐后说“我要开动了”“我吃饱了”的习惯，差不多也是在那个时候。我想这可能是通过学校教育推广出来的习惯，但重新翻阅当时的教育课本却没找到切实的依据。
以碗为船，以筷为桨
欧洲人用的餐具是盘子，就连汤也是装在汤盘里食用的，因此他们不说“喝”（drink）汤，而是“吃”（eat）汤。手持餐具、直接就口被视为失礼的行为，可将器皿直接就口的，只有茶、咖啡、酒之类的饮品。
欧洲人的食物必须以叉子或汤匙从餐具中取出，送入口中，不可借由食物让口与盘子直接接触。因此有些人吃日本面食时，对于以口就碗的吃法心理上会有些不舒服。
有句话说“以碗为船，以筷为桨”，在普遍使用筷子进食的东亚国家，碗形的餐具有很多，以碗盛饭和汤已是习惯。在中国，吃饭喝汤时以口就碗是被允许的，基本上配菜都装在共用的餐具内，所以不需要将餐具拿在手上，直接用筷子夹食即 可。
但在朝鲜半岛，手持餐具进食是禁忌，所有的料理要用筷子和汤匙取食。这么看来，日本人的用餐方式似乎显得很不礼 貌。
日本一直以来都没有使用汤匙吃东西的习惯，手持餐具进食是很常见的。所以，日本人很重视餐具拿在手中的感觉，以及就口时的触感。不光是视觉上要赏心悦目，方便使用的大小、肌肤接触到的感受、恰到好处的重量、稳定的重心等触觉也很重要。
越来越多的日本人会选购成对的碗，但有件事似乎正被大家遗忘——日本的碗有男碗与女碗之分。男碗的直径比女碗略大，高度也不同，就连夫妻对筷也是男性用的比较长。这并不是男女的差别待遇，而是配合男女手掌的大小，以方便使用为诉求，制作出符合人体学的优秀餐具。
作品简介
《日本的餐桌》，[日]石毛直道 著，连雪雅 译，浙江人民出版社，2017年8月
日本料理风靡全球，越来越多的国人也对日料产生兴趣，但日本的饮食文化我们却知之甚少。吃寿司时，谁会想到“板前”是厨师的称谓？又有多少人知道“出前一丁”是“外卖一份”的意思？日料，我们时常接触，但相关的历史渊源、文化意义，我们都未必真正了解。《日本的餐桌》正好提供这些看似平凡却容易被忽略的饮食信息。
作者石毛直道长期研究各种类型的饮食文化，在日本享誉盛名。在书中，他搜罗各种食材，以人类学的宏观角度，带领读者探索各种文化风貌，由农地走到食肆，从收割讲到烹调；地域上更从日本出发，探索亚洲，宏观世界各地的饮食渊源，中国的馒头、美国的莴苣、韩国的辣明太子，“东饮西食”无所不包。

https://www.forums.woodnet.net/showthrea...id=7334239
It was very difficult to get all of the angled M&T shoulders to line up with the angles on the base and support. I used loose tenons, 1/2-inch thick on 1.5-inch curved legs. Probably 200 fine-tune cuts shaving away the shoulders using my jig on the table saw. Notice the wedge, I would slide the wedge between the stops on the jig slightly to change the angle of the curved legs.
I will use hanger bolts to attach the base, using slots to account for wood movement.

posts.title: Евроассоциация аукнулась Украине ростом цен на молоко и мясо
posts.text: Зона свободной торговли с Европейским Союзом является одной из причин ускорения инфляции на Украине. Произошло это вследствие резкого роста экспорта мясомолочной продукции с Украины в страны ЕС на фоне снижения ее производства на Украине. На эту тенденцию в своем блоге обращает внимание украинский экономист Виктор Скаршевский. «Так, экспорт свинины в страны ЕС вырос в 2,6 раза (за 9 месяцев 2017 года), мяса крупного рогатого скота – на 39%, сливочного масла – в 2,7 раза и т.д. При этом производство свинины в Украине за тот же период сократилось на 1,6%, телятины – на 0,1%, а производство молока – на минус 1,8%. Добавим к этому и сокращение поголовья свиней на 8,3% и коров – на 1,9%», — пишет эксперт.Он указывает на парадоксальную ситуацию: Украина производит все меньше, но при этом увеличивает экспорт. «Именно этот «парадокс» и привел к тому, что цены на мясомолочную продукцию в Украине за 9 месяцев 2017 года выросли на 30%, что, в свою очередь, существенно повлияло на увеличение общего индекса инфляции» , — приходит к выводу Скаршевский.

posts.title: Erika's mom
posts.text:
Mom passed away Wednesday, November 1st @ 5:30pm. She past on All Saints Day and what would've been my grandma's birthday (her mom). A beautiful day to go home. ♡
*We had a memorial mass for her on Friday and will be taking her back home this weekend where she will be put to rest.
It feels unreal. I feel like I'm still on "work" mode with so much still to do with phone calls, funeral home, hospice, airline tickets, funeral I'm mexico, etc, that I don't think it has really sunken in. Only in small waves.
Although we had a rough night, we were able to get her comfortable pretty quick thanks to a hospice nurse who was there with us changing doses and frequency as needed. After she left in the morning, we were able to keep her comfortable as promised. My brother was able to fly back and get to her just in time as my other sister watched on video chat. (What great things we can achieve with technology today♡). As sad as it was and is, it was also beautiful. She was sorrounded by family and love. I gave her so many kisses....they might last me a while. She had an army of prayer warriors every where and I know she is now in the precense of the Lord free of this illness.
I also know that I am eternally grateful to all of you. Thank you for all your help, suggestions, experiences; for rejoicing in our little victories and hearing me in our darkest days during her journey. Thank you thank you thank you!!!!
-Erika
